<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>165</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>nǐ zǒng shì zhè yàng ài wǒ zhǔ 迦南165</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ zǒng shì zhè yàng ài wǒ zhǔ! huī xīn de shí hòu nǐ lái bāng zhù wǒ,
 nǐ zǒng shì zhè yàng ài wǒ zhǔ! shāng xīn de shí hòu nǐ lái ān wèi wǒ,
 wǒ zuì dà de bǎo zhàng jiù shì nǐ ya! yǒu nǐ wǒ píng ān zài yě bù jù pà
 wǒ zuì dà de cái fù jiù shì nǐ ya! yǒu nǐ wǒ mǎn zú zài yě bù quē fá
 rén shēng lǚ tú zhōng yǒu nǐ wǒ hái yào shén me
 gǎn ēn de lèi shuǐ shí shí yǒng shàng xīn tóu nǐ jiāng shēng mìng de dào lù zhǐ shì wǒ.</lyrics>
</song>